    <item>
      <title>०१</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/6/01/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/6/01/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/6/01/01_athAto_brahmANaM_brahmaRShim.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;०१ अथातो ब्रह्माणं ब्रह्मऋषिम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अथातो ब्रह्माणं ब्रह्मऋषिं ब्रह्मयोनिमिन्द्रं प्रजापतिं वसिष्ठं वामदेवं कहोलं कौषीतकिं महाकौषीतकिं सुयज्ञं शाङ्खायनमाश्वलायनमैतरेयं महैतरेयं कात्यायनं शाट्यायनं शाकल्यं बभ्रुं बाभ्रव्यं मण्डुं माण्डव्यं सर्वानेव पूर्वाचार्यान्नमस्य स्वाध्यायारण्यकस्य नियमानुदाहरिष्यामः&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/oldenberg/6/01/01_athAto_brahmANaM_brahmaRShim.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;1 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;. Now, after having paid reverence to Brahman, to the Brahmar̥shi, to (those who descend from) Brahman&amp;rsquo;s womb, to Indra, Prajāpati, Vasishṭḥa, Vāmadeva, Kahola Kaushītaki, Mahākaushītaki, Suyajña Śāṅkhāyana, Āśvalāyana, Aitareya, Mahaitareya, Kātyāyana, Śāṭyāyana, Śākalya, Babhru, Bābhravya, Maṇḍu, Māṇḍavya, and to all the teachers of the past, we will henceforth explain the rules for the Āraṇyaka as forming the subject of Svādhyāya (private recitation of a text).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०२</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/6/02/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/6/02/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/6/02/01_UrdhvamAShADhyAshchaturo_mAsAnnAdhIyItAtyantam.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;०१ ऊर्ध्वमाषाढ्याश्चतुरो मासान्नाधीयीतात्यन्तम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;ऊर्ध्वमाषाढ्याश्चतुरो मासान्नाधीयीतात्यन्तं शक्वर्य इति नियमाः २&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/oldenberg/6/02/01_UrdhvamAShADhyAshchaturo_mAsAnnAdhIyItAtyantam.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;During four months after the full moon of Âshâdha let him not study.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/6/02/02_shakvarya_iti_niyamAH.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;०२ शक्वर्य इति नियमाः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;शक्वर्य इति नियमाः २&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/oldenberg/6/02/02_shakvarya_iti_niyamAH.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;6 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . Especially the Śakvarī verses (are concerned by what has been declared). Such are the rules.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/6/02/03_prAgjyotiShamaparAjitAyAM_dishi_puNyamupagamya.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;०३ प्राग्ज्योतिषमपराजितायां दिशि पुण्यमुपगम्य ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;प्राग्ज्योतिषमपराजितायां दिशि पुण्यमुपगम्य देशम् ३&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०३</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/6/03/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/6/03/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/6/03/01_atha_pravishya_maNDalam.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;०१ अथ प्रविश्य मण्डलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अथ प्रविश्य मण्डलं १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/oldenberg/6/03/01_atha_pravishya_maNDalam.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Now after they have entered the circle -&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/6/03/02_prA~Nmukha_AchArya_upavishatyuda~NmukhA.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;०२ प्राङ्मुख आचार्य उपविशत्युदङ्मुखा ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;प्राङ्मुख आचार्य उपविशत्युदङ्मुखा दक्षिणत इतरे यथाप्रधानम् २&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/oldenberg/6/03/02_prA~Nmukha_AchArya_upavishatyuda~NmukhA.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;2 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . The teacher sits down with his face to the east, the others, according to their rank, (sit down) towards the south, with their faces to the north.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०४</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/6/04/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/6/04/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/6/04/01_adabdhaM_mana_iShiram.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;०१ अदब्धं मन इषिरम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अदब्धं मन इषिरं चक्षुः सूर्यो ज्योतिषां श्रेष्ठो दीक्षे मा मा हिँ सीरिति सवितारमीक्षन्ते १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/oldenberg/6/04/01_adabdhaM_mana_iShiram.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;1 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . &amp;lsquo;Unerring mind, vigorous eye (is) the sun, the noblest of the stars. Inauguration, do no harm to me!&amp;rsquo; - with (these words) they look at Savitṛ (I.e. the sun).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/6/04/02_yuvaM_surAmamityekA_svasti.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;०२ युवं सुराममित्येका स्वस्ति ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;युवं सुराममित्येका स्वस्ति नः पथ्यास्विति च तिस्र इति महाव्रतस्य २&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०५</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/6/05/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/6/05/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/6/05/01_tamahamAtmanItyAtmAnamabhinihitaM_trirhitam.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;०१ तमहमात्मनीत्यात्मानमभिनिहितं त्रिर्हितम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;तमहमात्मनीत्यात्मानमभिनिहितं त्रिर्हितम् १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/oldenberg/6/05/01_tamahamAtmanItyAtmAnamabhinihitaM_trirhitam.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;1 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;. &amp;lsquo;That (I place) within myself&amp;rsquo; - with (these words they turn their thoughts to the universal) Self that is placed (within themselves?) three times repeated (?).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/6/05/02_upa_mA_shrIrjuShatAmupa.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;०२ उप मा श्रीर्जुषतामुप ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;उप मा श्रीर्जुषतामुप यशोऽनु मा श्रीर्जुषतामनु यशः २&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/oldenberg/6/05/02_upa_mA_shrIrjuShatAmupa.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;With (the formula), &amp;lsquo;May happiness rejoice in me and glory; may happiness rejoice with me and glory; -&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/6/05/03_sendraH_sagaNaH_sabalaH.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;०३ सेन्द्रः सगणः सबलः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;सेन्द्रः सगणः सबलः सयशः सवीर्य उत्तिष्ठानीत्युत्तिष्ठति ३&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०६</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAnkhAyanam/sUtram/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/6/06/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
